cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.CL 

The paper proposes a deep unsupervised clustering method using autoencoders, which is a common technique in machine learning and falls under the category of cs.LG (Machine Learning). The method is applied to image data, which suggests that it could also fall under cs.CV (Computer Vision). The use of autoencoders also suggests that it could fall under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Finally, the paper mentions the use of natural language processing, which could suggest a connection to cs.CL (Computation and Language).
